**As a** developer  
**I need** to create an account microservice to keep track of the customers on e-commerce website  
**So that** customers can use REST API to call on other microservices   
      
### Details and Assumptions
    * Maintain customers e-commerce website
    * The service only needs read, update, delete, and list customers
    
### Acceptance Criteria     
    gherkin 
    Given the task for development microsevices
    When there is an other team already developed the database model with an endpoint
    Then I only add the REST APIs to make it workable
